    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/Super-SpatialTitle.gif?t=1734221353\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an infinite universe of diverse planets and star systems! Warp across the universe, discover the remnants of a previous civilization, and build machines and structures to help you not only survive, but thrive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/08866dbd18d08e37229b441c7e01c89d.poster.avif?t=1734221353\" width=800 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/08866dbd18d08e37229b441c7e01c89d.webm?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/08866dbd18d08e37229b441c7e01c89d.mp4?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are all on your own, left to discover the properties of both planet and machine and use them to the best of your ability. There are infinite star systems accessible through the warp-drive of your space ship. Each star system has varying unique and colorful planets with different characteristics, visuals, and resources. Where will you set up your base, and where will you strip for resources?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/c2f645508cc9b804fbc51557a5563300.poster.avif?t=1734221353\" width=800 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/c2f645508cc9b804fbc51557a5563300.webm?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/c2f645508cc9b804fbc51557a5563300.mp4?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with a fun physics based item/inventory system! Collect resources and craft them into new, useful components, machines, and buildings. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/323febed068a6d6979dae0d05a98f310.poster.avif?t=1734221353\" width=800 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/323febed068a6d6979dae0d05a98f310.webm?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168380/extras/323febed068a6d6979dae0d05a98f310.mp4?t=1734221353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a simple cozy home, or an elaborate system of automated machines. Each structure can be colored to your specifications.</p>",
